    <item>
      <title>墨西哥当局称，窃贼杀死三名冲浪者以偷他们的卡车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/mexican-authorities-say-thieves-killed-2-australians-and-an-american-to-steal-their-truck</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥城（美联社）——当局周日表示，窃贼在前往墨西哥冲浪时杀害了两名澳大利亚人和一名美国人，目的是偷走他们的卡车，特别是因为他们想要轮胎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/mexican-authorities-say-thieves-killed-2-australians-and-an-american-to-steal-their-truck</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 19:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平抵达巴黎 法国加大电动汽车雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/france-ramps-up-electric-vehicle-ambition-as-xi-arrives-in-paris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府将于周一与汽车行业签署一项内容广泛的协议，为电动汽车销售设定新目标，恰逢中国国家主席习近平抵达该行业进行国事访问，该行业的贸易紧张局势笼罩着阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/france-ramps-up-electric-vehicle-ambition-as-xi-arrives-in-paris</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对美国国会议员的贿赂指控牵涉墨西哥阿兹特克公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/bribery-charge-against-us-congressman-implicates-mexico-s-azteca</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法庭文件显示，墨西哥阿兹台克银行的一名高管帮助安排向美国众议院民主党人德克萨斯州的亨利·奎利亚尔及其妻子付款，以换取在华盛顿的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/bribery-charge-against-us-congressman-implicates-mexico-s-azteca</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 17:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
